data.description: Discover this expansive 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home nestled in the Brookshaven South. A custom-built beauty, this residence is set on a 1.40-acre lot. As you enter the inviting foyer, you're welcomed into a cozy living room adorned with a fireplace featuring an antique mantel and beautiful hardwood floors. The formal dining room boasts hardwood floors and an elegant chandelier. The spacious kitchen, with custom-built cabinets, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, is tiled for both style and practicality. The large master bedroom features a tray ceiling and an ensuite master bath with a separate tub and tiled shower, complemented by two generous closets. Upstairs, a media room awaits, accompanied by a large bedroom and bathroom. Out back you'll enjoy the screened-in back porch, ideal for relaxing. Notably, this property offers a scenic view of the lake located at the rear of the 1.40-acre expanse. Conveniently located only 30 minutes from the new Hyundai Plant!
